<h1><em>quantifier (period)</em> @HI{{ni}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<ol>
<li> @EM{{<em>quantifier (period)</em> @HI{{ni}}}} -@KJ{{-times}}V
</ol>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
This sentence pattern is used to indicate how often something is done.
</p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      1 @HI{{ka@KJ{{month}}@EM{{ni}} 2@KJ{{-times reflect^brush-stroke}}wo @KJ{{see}}masu.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      I go to see films twice a month.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>

